<item>
            <title>[FELIX-4010] SCR Plugin aborts when scanning a Java 8 class file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4010</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like the ASM library referred to by the SCR plugin is not compatible with Java 8 class file version 52.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How to reproduce: Use Java 8 to run a maven based project build where at least one of the @Component annotated classes extend (or implement) a Java 8 runtime provided class, e.g. java.io.Serializable, in class file version 52.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12640259">FELIX-4010</key>
            <summary>SCR Plugin aborts when scanning a Java 8 class file</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
